{"tid":1456640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK：機場大批市民陸續離開","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:35:55.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a427a37c22276df53da24a2802f85327a8d2bcdb","tid":1456640,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"機場大批市民陸續離開　巴士及機鐵站站滿候車市民<br />\n<br />\n較早前聚集在機場的大批市民已經陸續離開，機場一號客運大樓的巴士站及機鐵站，都站滿等待巴士及列車的市民。接機大堂及離境大堂內聚集的市民明顯減少，仍然留守的市民，則不時於接機大堂高叫口號，例如「Stand with Hong Kong」。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-12 18:28:44"},{"pid":"7cf43a9fe72945ba27219158a5ec95cdd2f0d0f2","tid":1456640,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8932e6bb304d3acd67b03970ee60c5662f525a76","tid":1456640,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}